social_posts.post_text: Making this made me realize, WOW, it’s been a busy and amazing year. I’m so insanely grateful for all the people I’ve worked with and connections I’ve made this year, the tears I’ve cried, the stress I’ve gotten through, the people who kept me sane. I’m so lucky to love what I do and there’s no other career I would want to call mine. My expectations for myself are extremely high and this is the start. Just like that, another year passes and I can’t wait to see what successes and challenges 2023 holds. Thank you.
